CRUD PRODUCT API

View      GET  http://localhost:8080/api/products
View Page GET  http://localhost:8080/api/products/page (TÃ¬m trang key = page, value = 1)
Create product   POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
          {
              "nameProduct": "Iphone AAA",
              "price": 12000,
              "idPeople": 4
          }
Update product   PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/2
          {
              "nameProduct": "Samsung Note JSF1",
              "price": 22000,
              "idPeople": 2
          }
Delete product   DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Price near       GET    http://localhost:8080/api/products/near-price/10000/15000
Search name      GET    http://localhost:8080/api/products/search-name/I